    <item>
      <title>如果当选总统，加纳巴武米亚将把塞地与黄金挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ghana-s-bawumia-to-link-cedi-to-gold-if-elected-president-lzljaq5j</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚 (Mahamudu Bawumia) 表示，如果他在 12 月赢得总统大选，他将采用将塞地货币与黄金挂钩的新汇率制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ghana-s-bawumia-to-link-cedi-to-gold-if-elected-president-lzljaq5j</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
